body_html: @louisquinn Thank you. My Friday looks a bit weird but I will try to get to this and have some response (like an update :-) on progress and what I am finding and thinking) before EOD Monday 22-JAN. A complexity is loading the graph vs. the code and the object detection code is not maintained by the TensorFlow team. I will see if I can discern something from the data I collect. I am looking to setup a decent inference test and while this may not be it, the outcome may be useful to you and others.
